headline: Montana Capital Partners announces final close of MCP Opportunity Secondary Program VI (OSP VI)
summary: BAAR-ZUG, Switzerland, February 11, 2026--OSP VI closed with a total programme size of US$1.4billion, in line with OSP VI’s most recent predecessor fund.
